Package client.models.mapdata

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Board
    Holds pointers to important map data:
    Hexes, ports, locations of cities, settlements,
    roads, and robber
    EdgeLocation
    Holds x and y coordinates of edge, along with direction
    EdgeValue
    Holds number of player that owns road on edge.
    Hex
    Hex holds location on map, resource, and number token
    HexLocation
    Holds x and y coordinates of hex
    Port
    Port object contains data of hex location, direction, trade resource, and ratio
